Banyo zamanınız geldi teğmen.

744
00:57:45,424 --> 00:57:46,758
Harper!

745
00:57:49,970 --> 00:57:52,431
Cooper, Larson,

746
00:57:54,641 --> 00:57:55,976
Webster,

747
00:57:57,352 --> 00:58:00,856
- Gump. Gump.
